longBusinessSummary: Ddev Plastiks Industries Limited manufactures and sells plastic compounds in India and internationally. The company offers antifab, filled compounds, and master batches used in packaging industries for making woven and cement bags; PVC compounds used in wire and cable, and construction industries; halogen free flame retardant (HFFR); water tree retardant (WTR) XLPE for cables insulation; and sioplas, XLPE compounds, semicons, and EHV compounds. It also offers engineering plastic compounds used in the white goods, automotive, and electrical appliances industries; XL HFFR (cross linkable HFFR) compounds used for applications in solar and photovoltaic cables; anti-fibrillation compound; PVC compounds cables; poly vinyl chloride; and polyethylene. In addition, the company provides PE compounds, footwear compounds, pipe compounds, peroxide compounds, PP (polypropylene) compounds, and mineral field compounds. It also exports its products. The company was founded in 1977 and is headquartered in Kolkata, India. Ddev Plastiks Industries Limited is a subsidiary of Bbigplas Poly Private Limited.
